Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, raspi-utils-core
Description: Semtech SX1302 LoRa concentrator HAL and packet forwarder
 Hardware Abstraction Layer and utilities for the Semtech SX1302
 LoRa concentrator, including lora_pkt_fwd packet forwarder,
 chip ID utility, spectral scan, and network downlink tools.
 .
 Patched for Raspberry Pi on Debian Trixie with pinctrl GPIO
 support and improved GPS NMEA parsing.
